column1: SELECT song_name FROM song WHERE rating BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND resolution = 10 ORDER BY song_name DESC;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s.artist_name), g.most_popular_in FROM song s JOIN genre g ON s.genre_is = g.g_name GROUP BY g.most_popular_in HAVING COUNT(s.song_name) >= 67;
SELECT MIN(o.f_id), COUNT(DISTINCT o.f_id), COUNT(DISTINCT o.formats), o.file_size FROM files AS o WHERE  o.f_id < 94 GROUP BY o.file_size, o.f_id HAVING COUNT(o.f_id) = 39 LIMIT 9

SELECT AVG(CAST(REPLACE(REPLACE(file_size, "MB", ""), "GB", "") AS REAL)), f_id FROM files JOIN artist JOIN genre ON artist.preferred_genre = genre.g_name AND files.artist_name = artist.artist_name GROUP BY f_id;

SELECT SUM(CAST(genre.rating AS NUMBER)), genre.rating FROM files JOIN song JOIN artist JOIN genre ON artist.preferred_genre = genre.g_name AND artist.artist_name = song.artist_name AND song.genre_is = genre.g_name AND files.artist_name = artist.artist_name WHERE CAST(genre.rating AS NUMBER) BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  CAST(genre.rating AS NUMBER) < 87
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT genre_is) FROM song JOIN artist ON artist.artist_name = song.artist_name WHERE (resolution BETWEEN 1 AND 10) OR resolution >= 81 LIMIT 1

SELECT preferred_genre FROM song JOIN artist JOIN genre ON artist.preferred_genre = genre.g_name AND artist.artist_name = song.artist_name AND song.genre_is = genre.g_name WHERE artist.country < (SELECT MAX(country) FROM song WHERE rating BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  resolution <= 49) ORDER BY preferred_genre DESC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT a.releasedate), a.rating FROM song AS a WHERE a.resolution BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND a.f_id <= 50

SELECT T3.resolution FROM song AS T3 JOIN artist AS T1 JOIN genre AS T2 ON T1.preferred_genre = T2.g_name AND T1.artist_name = T3.artist_name AND T3.genre_is = T2.g_name WHERE T3.rating BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  T2.rating >= "28" ORDER BY T3.resolution DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT r.resolution, r.languages FROM song AS r WHERE r.f_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10

SELECT files.f_id, artist.artist_name FROM files JOIN artist ON files.artist_name = artist.artist_name JOIN song ON song.artist_name = artist.artist_name JOIN genre ON artist.preferred_genre = genre.g_name AND song.genre_is = genre.g_name WHERE files.f_id <= 78;

SELECT T4.languages, T1.g_name FROM genre AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.g_name = T2.genre_is JOIN artist AS T3 ON T2.artist_name = T3.artist_name AND T3.preferred_genre = T1.g_name JOIN files AS T4 ON T3.artist_name = T4.artist_name WHERE T4.f_id > 49;
SELECT artist.artist_name FROM artist JOIN files ON files.artist_name = artist.artist_name JOIN song ON song.artist_name = artist.artist_name AND song.f_id = files.f_id;
SELECT AVG(f_id) FROM files JOIN artist ON files.artist_name = artist.artist_name WHERE  f_id > 55
SELECT COUNT(f_id), COUNT(DISTINCT formats), COUNT(DISTINCT formats) FROM files WHERE f_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  f_id < 52 LIMIT 4

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T3.languages), T2.gender FROM artist AS T2 INNER JOIN files AS T1 ON T1.artist_name = T2.artist_name INNER JOIN song AS T3 ON T3.f_id = T1.f_id WHERE T3.resolution >= 41 GROUP BY T2.gender HAVING COUNT(T3.resolution) < 79
